groups.description:
The achievement endpoints will return information on achievements completed by
the user. Achievements may be unlocked by completing certain challenges, such as
answering all questions for a given category. Users can track their progress towards
completing an achievement, and will unlock premium points upon completion.

When an achievement is unlocked, a Firebase notification will be sent to the user's
device. For this to work, the Firebase device registration token [will need to be
set](#users-token-update). The Firebase notifications will then have the following format:

```json
{
    "message": {
        "token": "bk3RNwTe3H0:CI2k_HHwgIpoDKCIZvvDMExUdFQ3P1...",
        "notification": {
            "title": "Trophe freigeschaltet: Neu hier?",
            "body": "Schlieen Sie Ihr erstes Spiel ab"
        },
        "data": {
            "achievement_id": "1"
        }
    }
}
```

